behavior observe_chicken(chicken:item):
    body:
        observe(chicken, "Check if the chicken can be sliced")

behavior slice_chicken(chicken:item, cutting_board:item, knife:item):
    body:
        achieve_once inhand(knife)
        achieve close(chicken, cutting_board)
        achieve cut(chicken)

behavior __goal__():

        bind chicken: item where:
            is_food_chicken(chicken) and clean(chicken)
        bind knife: item where:
            is_knife(knife)
        bind cutting_board: item where:
            is_cutting_board(cutting_board)
        observe_chicken(chicken)
        slice_chicken(chicken, cutting_board, knife)
